::GoldenEye::

She saw him step out of the CR chamber.  She smiled.  She was happy 
to see that he was alright. She stated to say somwthing when he 
hugged her.  She put her arms around him and hugged him back.  She 
was enjoying his touch again.  She felt her spark race as he hugged 
her.  She had missed him and had been worried for him beyond 
compare.  She whipsered to him,"Glad to have you back.  You were 
missed."
